#: ../../source/baselines.rst:2
msgid "Baseline Solvers"
msgstr "基准求解器"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:4
msgid ""
"All baseline solvers are implemented in "
"``src/funsearch_cvrp/cvrp/baselines.py``. Each solver takes a "
":class:`CVRPInstance` and returns ``list[list[int]]`` — a list of routes,"
" where each route is an ordered list of customer indices (depot not "
"included)."
msgstr ""
"所有基准求解器均实现于 ``src/funsearch_cvrp/cvrp/baselines.py``。"
"每个求解器接受一个 :class:`CVRPInstance`，返回 ``list[list[int]]``——"
"路线列表，每条路线为客户索引的有序列表（不含仓库节点）。"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:9
msgid "Nearest Neighbor"
msgstr "最近邻算法"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:11
msgid ""
"Greedy construction heuristic. At each step, the vehicle moves to the "
"nearest unserved customer that fits within remaining capacity. When no "
"feasible customer exists, the route ends and a new vehicle departs from "
"the depot."
msgstr ""
"贪心构造启发式算法。每一步选择距当前位置最近且满足剩余容量的未服务客户。"
"当无可行客户时，当前路线结束，新车辆从仓库出发。"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:15
msgid "**Time complexity**: :math:`O(n^2)` per instance."
msgstr "时间复杂度：每个实例 :math:`O(n^2)`。"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:17
msgid ""
"**Weakness**: Greedy choices early in a route can force long detours "
"later."
msgstr "**缺点**：路线前期的贪心选择可能导致后期出现较长绕路。"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:25
msgid "Clarke-Wright Savings"
msgstr "Clarke-Wright 节约算法"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:27
msgid ""
"Constructive heuristic based on the savings algorithm (Clarke & Wright, "
"1964)."
msgstr "基于节约算法（Clarke & Wright, 1964）的构造式启发算法。"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:29
msgid ""
"**Idea**: Start with one dedicated vehicle per customer (depot → customer"
" → depot). Merging two routes :math:`(\\ldots, i)` and :math:`(j, "
"\\ldots)` saves:"
msgstr ""
"**思路**：初始为每个客户分配一辆专属车辆（仓库 → 客户 → 仓库）。"
"合并路线 :math:`(\\ldots, i)` 与 :math:`(j, \\ldots)` 的节约值为："

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:32
msgid "s_{ij} = c_{i,\\text{depot}} + c_{\\text{depot},j} - c_{ij}"
msgstr "s_{ij} = c_{i,\\text{depot}} + c_{\\text{depot},j} - c_{ij}"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:36
msgid ""
"Routes are merged in decreasing order of savings, subject to capacity "
"constraints and the requirement that the merged customers are at the ends"
" of their respective routes (parallel Clarke-Wright variant)."
msgstr ""
"按节约值从大到小依次合并路线，需满足容量约束，"
"且被合并的客户必须位于各自路线的端点（并行 Clarke-Wright 变体）。"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:40
msgid ""
"**Time complexity**: :math:`O(n^2 \\log n)` (dominated by sorting savings"
" list)."
msgstr "时间复杂度：:math:`O(n^2 \\log n)`（瓶颈为节约值列表排序）。"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:48
msgid "2-opt Local Search"
msgstr "2-opt 局部搜索"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:50
msgid ""
"Post-processing improvement applied independently to each route. "
"Repeatedly reverses sub-sequences of a route while the reversal reduces "
"total route distance. Stops when no improving swap exists."
msgstr ""
"对每条路线独立进行后处理优化。反复翻转路线中的子序列，"
"直到不存在能缩短路线距离的交换为止。"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:54
msgid ""
"\\Delta = d(r_{i-1}, r_j) + d(r_i, r_{j+1}) - d(r_{i-1}, r_i) - d(r_j, "
"r_{j+1})"
msgstr ""
"\\Delta = d(r_{i-1}, r_j) + d(r_i, r_{j+1}) - d(r_{i-1}, r_i) - d(r_j, "
"r_{j+1})"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:58
msgid "A swap is accepted when :math:`\\Delta < 0`."
msgstr "当 :math:`\\Delta < 0` 时接受交换。"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:60
msgid ""
"**Note**: 2-opt only reorders customers within a route — it does not move"
" customers between routes."
msgstr "**注意**：2-opt 仅在路线内部重排客户顺序，不会将客户移至其他路线。"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:74
msgid "Composing with ``with_two_opt``"
msgstr "使用 ``with_two_opt`` 组合"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:76
msgid ""
"``with_two_opt`` is a decorator that wraps any solver with a 2-opt post-"
"processing step:"
msgstr "``with_two_opt`` 是一个装饰器，可为任意求解器附加 2-opt 后处理步骤："

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:86
msgid "Weighted Greedy"
msgstr "加权贪心算法"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:88
msgid ""
"Generalisation of the nearest-neighbor heuristic parameterised by three "
"weights :math:`(w_1, w_2, w_3)`. At each step the next customer is chosen"
" to maximise:"
msgstr ""
"最近邻启发式的推广，由三个权重 :math:`(w_1, w_2, w_3)` 参数化。"
"每步选择使以下评分最大的客户："

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:91
msgid ""
"\\text{score}(c) = w_1 \\cdot (-d_{\\text{cur},c}) + w_2 \\cdot "
"\\frac{d_c}{Q} + w_3 \\cdot (-d_{c,\\text{depot}})"
msgstr ""
"\\text{score}(c) = w_1 \\cdot (-d_{\\text{cur},c}) + w_2 \\cdot "
"\\frac{d_c}{Q} + w_3 \\cdot (-d_{c,\\text{depot}})"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:95
msgid ""
"where :math:`d_{\\text{cur},c}` is distance from current position, "
":math:`d_c / Q` is the demand ratio, and :math:`d_{c,\\text{depot}}` is "
"distance from customer to depot."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`d_{\\text{cur},c}` 为当前位置到客户的距离，"
":math:`d_c / Q` 为需求比例，"
":math:`d_{c,\\text{depot}}` 为客户到仓库的距离。"

#: ../../source/baselines.rst:98
msgid ""
"Setting :math:`w_1=1, w_2=0, w_3=0` recovers the nearest-neighbor "
"heuristic. The weights are the search target for the sample-efficient "
"search in ``src/funsearch_cvrp/search/``."
msgstr ""
"当 :math:`w_1=1, w_2=0, w_3=0` 时退化为最近邻算法。"
"这三个权重是 ``src/funsearch_cvrp/search/`` 中样本高效搜索的优化目标。"

